WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Install the TypeScript SDK package in your wallet project.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Create a BridgeClient with your API base URL and API key.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Get a quote and prepare an unsigned funding transaction for the user to sign.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Submit the signed XDR and poll transaction status until success.
